Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.88,0:01:21.00,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}从今往后的事 I will be there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:26.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}那天以后的事 With me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.22,0:01:31.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}夕阳西下之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.34,0:01:36.80,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}追逐着渐渐消失的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:42.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}谁都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.34,0:01:46.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}时光无法回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:51.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}呈现在眼前的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:55.88,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}毫无疑问的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.30,0:02:05.30,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}真正想见的人 在道路的另一头
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:08.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}为了追逐那天的你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}迈出了脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:18.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}这前面是无法成歌的Stories
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:22.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}I can’t tell what’s going on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:29.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}现在还不是寻找答案的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:34.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}现在已经无需用声音表达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:39.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)\blur4}只要怀着心愿向前
